title: Jaz & Jul's Chocolate House
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Take-out, British, English
description: Vegetarian cafe where all menu items contain a form of chocolate. Offers a small food menu with dishes like black bean chili, salad, toast with avocado or pesto, and banana bread. Drinks are made with almond milk and have vegan whipped cream and marshmallow. Opened Nov 2016.
